30962008/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Left+Atrial+Appendage+Occlusion+for+The+Unmet+Clinical+Needs+of+Stroke+Prevention+in+Nonvalvular+Atrial+Fibrillation&amp;author=DR+Holmes&amp;author=M+Alkhouli&amp;author=V+Reddy&amp;publication_year=2019&amp;journal=Mayo+Clin+Proc&amp;pages=864-874&amp;doi=10.1016%2Fj.mayocp.2018.09.025&amp;pmid=30962008">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">6.</div><div id="r6" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Holmes DR Jr, Kar S, Price MJ, et al. Prospective randomized evaluation of the Watchman Left Atrial Appendage Closure device in patients with atrial fibrillation versus long-term warfarin therapy: the PREVAIL trial. <em>J Am Coll Cardiol</em> 2014;64(1):1–12 [Published correction appears in J Am Coll Cardiol 2014;64(11):1186.].</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.jacc.2014.04.029">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/24998121/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Prospective+randomized+evaluation+of+the+Watchman+Left+Atrial+Appendage+Closure+device+in+patients+with+atrial+fibrillation+versus+long-term+warfarin+therapy%3A+the+PREVAIL+trial&amp;author=DR+Holmes&amp;author=S+Kar&amp;author=MJ+Price&amp;publication_year=2014&amp;journal=J+Am+Coll+Cardiol&amp;pages=1-12&amp;doi=10.1016%2Fj.jacc.2014.04.029&amp;pmid=24998121">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">7.</div><div id="r7" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Holmes DR Jr, Doshi SK, Kar S, et al. Left Atrial Appendage Closure as an Alternative to Warfarin for Stroke Prevention in Atrial Fibrillation: A Patie